Story:

Seki, a young japanese detective has lost his workmate whom was killed by a serial killer. This weird killer enjoys killing a particular type of person - the transexual. When the killer escapes to Thailand, Seki follows and meets Lily, a cabaret showgirl who her (or his?) best friend was murdered by the same killer. Lily is the only witness who saw the killer&#039;s face, and is in danger. Fortunately, Seki rescues her in time. Meanwhile, Lily helps Seki from being killed, so they become friends. Then, the two team up to hunt the killer before he will bomb a big carnival festival where the transexuals gather.
